- pug_html += app.breadcrumbs('Startup Business Valuation Calculator', 'finish', [ ['Home', '/'], ["What's My Business Worth?", '/calculator/BusinessValuation'], ["Startup Business Valuation Calculator", ''],]);


.container.calculator-container
  .row
    .offset-lg-2.col-lg-8
      ul.list-inline.top-breadcrambs.mb45.revenue-share-calculator
        li
          a(href="/calculator/capitalraise/intro").btn
            h4.text-uppercase.m-b-0 Intro
        li
          a(href="/calculator/capitalraise/step-1").btn
            h4.text-uppercase.m-b-0 step 1
        li
          a(href="/calculator/capitalraise/finish").current.btn
            h4.text-uppercase.m-b-0 finish

  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6.text-xs-center.p-l-0.p-r-0
      h2.m0.finish-calc.font-weight-light
        .like-detail-icon.d-inline-block
          i(aria-hidden="true").fa.fa-diamond.like-icon-circle
        | &nbsp;Based on your inputs, you may want to consider a valuation of
        | &nbsp;#{app.helpers.format.formatMoney(Math.round(data.PreMoneyValuation / 1000) * 1000)}

  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6.mt45
      p.text-justify  Please note, valuing a pre-revenue company is really more of an art than a science and can vary across a wide band, so if you derive a different valuation, that's ok. Just remember, valuation matters to potential investors, so if you want to increase the probability of success, try to ensure the value proposition is fair to everybody involved.

  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6
      hr.mt50.mb50

  .row
    .offset-lg-3.col-lg-6.text-xs-center
      a(href="/calculator/capitalraise/step-1").btn.btn-primary.text-uppercase back